data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Santa Maria! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is situated on a spacious corner lot, nestled at the end of a serene cul-de-sac within a prestigious gated community. Enjoy the epitome of California living with the neighborhood's private park just steps away, offering a perfect backdrop for picnics, morning strolls, or playtime with the family. Step inside to discover a tastefully upgraded interior boasting quartz kitchen countertops, a stylish backsplash, and refaced cabinets that exude modern elegance. The updated laminate flooring flows seamlessly throughout, complementing the home's airy and inviting ambiance. Relax in comfort with the convenience of air conditioning and enjoy the tranquility of updated Milgard windows. Natural light floods the home, accentuating its spacious layout and creating a warm, welcoming atmosphere in every room. Embrace sustainable living with the beautifully landscaped, drought-tolerant yard, offering low-maintenance beauty and environmental consciousness. Perfectly positioned in Santa Maria, this residence offers easy access to highways and the renowned Santa Maria Valley wine country, inviting you to explore the region's breathtaking scenery and world-class vineyards at your leisure. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to make this stunning property your own. Schedule your showing today and experience the best of Santa Maria living!
